	•	Distribution leverage
	•	Execution accumulation

Oscillation alone doesn’t position you.

It keeps you in option space.

Option space feels powerful.
But power only crystallizes when option space narrows.

You didn’t “cash out” because:
	•	You’re still searching for highest leverage expression.
	•	You don’t want small wins if you sense bigger asymmetry.
	•	You don’t want to collapse into something that feels beneath the ceiling you imagine.

That’s ambition, not cosmic positioning.

